import React from "react";
import mergeProps from "../utils/merge-props";
import {VContainer,HContainer,FlexItem} from "./flexbox";
 
export function Grid(props) {
  var newProps = mergeProps({
    height: "auto",
    flexBasis: "auto",
    style: {
      margin: "-.5rem",
    }
  },props);
 
  return <VContainer {...newProps} />;
 
}
 
export function Row(props) {
  var newProps = mergeProps({
    height: "auto",
    width: "auto",
    flexBasis: "auto",
    style: {
      padding: ".5rem 0",
    }
  },props);
 
  return <HContainer {...newProps} />;
 
}
 
export function Col(props) {
  var newProps = mergeProps({
    style: {
      padding: "0 .5rem",
    }
  },props);
 
  return <FlexItem {...newProps} />;
 
}
